                <MadCap:snippetText src="../../../Resources/Snippets/task steps/Applications_Applications.flsnp" />
            </li>
            <li>Search for and select your app instance.</li>
            <li>
                Go to the <span class="uicontrol">Governance</span> tab.</li>
            <li>
				Go to the <span class="uicontrol">Policy</span> tab.
			</li>
            <li>
                <p>Open the <span class="uicontrol">Actions</span> dropdown menu associated with a rule.</p>
                <p>If you’re editing a policy, click <span class="uicontrol">Edit policy</span> or <span class="uicontrol">Continue editing policy</span> before you open the <span class="uicontrol">Actions</span> dropdown menu associated with a rule. </p>
                <p>Clicking <span class="uicontrol">Edit policy</span> creates a copy of the active policy in Draft mode.</p>
            </li>
